social_posts.post_text:
an old self portrait. when i get a new camera, these will return.

------

devoted to my slow, soft life. 

less internet. more reading, writing, listening, self care, bonding with real people in real life, cherishing my family and cherishing the silent gifts of life. 

this world moves so fast and i accept that its not in my nature to keep up. 

instead, i make choices that honor timeless creativity
